{"total":10,"pageSize":10,"pageCount":1,"data":[{"title":"","slug":"flag_in_your_hand1","date":"2020-12-28T12:37:55.565Z","updated":"2020-12-28T12:38:06.572Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/flag_in_your_hand1.json","excerpt":"","keywords":null,"cover":"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20201228195218456.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3dlaXhpbl80NjIyNzAxNg==,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70#pic_center","content":"<p><a href=\"https://adworld.xctf.org.cn/task/answer?type=crypto&number=5&grade=1&id=4869&page=1\">flag_in_your_hand</a><br>本题的附加为一个html网页和对于的js源码，直接用浏览器打开页面，<br><img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20201228195218456.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3dlaXhpbl80NjIyNzAxNg==,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70#pic_center\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\"></p>\n<p>使用浏览器的调试功能，可以观察具体的运行过程，略过复杂度的转换过程，可以发现输入的字符串都会经过ck函数<br><img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20201228195158430.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3dlaXhpbl80NjIyNzAxNg==,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70#pic_center\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\"></p>\n<p>进行判断，如果为判断结果为真，就可以得到flag，简单计算得到对应的字符串，输入得到最后的flag<br><img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20201228195419888.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3dlaXhpbl80NjIyNzAxNg==,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70#pic_center\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\"></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>crypto类型的题目可能会涉及多方面知识，以后应该学习各个方向的知识，才能更好的解决问题</p>\n</blockquote>\n","text":"flag_in_your_hand<br>本题的附加为一个html网页和对于的js源码，直接用浏览器打开页面，<br> [Figure] crypto类型的题目可能会涉及多方面知识，以后应该学习各个方向的知识，才能更好的解决问题","link":"","raw":null,"photos":[],"categories":[],"tags":[]},{"title":"","slug":"keyboard","date":"2020-12-28T12:37:30.657Z","updated":"2020-12-28T12:37:35.176Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/keyboard.json","excerpt":"","keywords":null,"cover":null,"content":"<p><a href=\"https://adworld.xctf.org.cn/task/answer?type=crypto&number=5&grade=1&id=4929&page=1\">告诉你个秘密</a></p>\n<p>附件为一个txt文件，里面内容只有2行</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>636A56355279427363446C4A49454A7154534230526D6843<br>56445A31614342354E326C4B4946467A5769426961453067</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>观察发现里面所有的字符，都不大于F，所以可以首先尝试将其按照ascii的十六进制解码得到另一串字符串</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>cjV5RyBscDlJIEJqTSB0RmhCVDZ1aCB5N2lKIFFzWiBiaE0g</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>字符串中出现了字母数字组合，且没有不可见字母，所以使用base64解码</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>r5yG lp9I BjM tFhBT6uh y7iJ QsZ bhM </p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>有明显的分组特征，经过观察发现其在键盘上的位置刚好可以围住一些字母，按照这种规则走下去，可以得到一个意义的字符串，也就是flag</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>TONGYUAN</p>\n</blockquote>\n","text":"告诉你个秘密附件为一个txt文件，里面内容只有2行636A56355279427363446C4A49454A7154534230526D6843<br>56445A31614342354E326C4B4946467A5769426961453067观察发现里面所有的字符，都不大","link":"","raw":null,"photos":[],"categories":[],"tags":[]},{"title":"","slug":"sherlock","date":"2020-12-28T12:37:03.723Z","updated":"2020-12-28T12:37:07.317Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/sherlock.json","excerpt":"","keywords":null,"cover":"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20201228202120577.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3dlaXhpbl80NjIyNzAxNg==,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70#pic_center","content":"<p><a href=\"https://adworld.xctf.org.cn/task/answer?type=crypto&number=5&grade=1&id=5526&page=1\">sherlock</a></p>\n<p>附件为一篇小说，首先采用搜索方法，直接搜索ｆｌａｇ，并没有什么发现，但是<img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20201228202120577.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3dlaXhpbl80NjIyNzAxNg==,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70#pic_center\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\"><br>发现大写字符在文件内容是随机出现的,利用python提取出其中所有的大写字母</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p></p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>是文字的01串,将其转化成二进制数,再转化为十六进制,对应ascii解码得到flag的字符串.</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>0x424954534354467b683164335f316e5f706c34316e5f353137337d</p>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<p>BITSCTF{h1d3_1n_pl41n_5173}</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>脚本如下:</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">f=<span class=\"built_in\">open</span>(<span class=\"string\">&#x27;c.txt&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\">lines=f.read()</span><br><span class=\"line\">t=[]</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">for</span> i <span class=\"keyword\">in</span> lines:</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">for</span> j <span class=\"keyword\">in</span> i:</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"string\">&#x27;A&#x27;</span>&lt;=i&lt;=<span class=\"string\">&#x27;Z&#x27;</span>:</span><br><span class=\"line\">            t.append(j)</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">s=<span class=\"string\">&#x27;&#x27;</span>.join(t)</span><br><span class=\"line\">print(s)</span><br><span class=\"line\">f=<span class=\"string\">&#x27;&#x27;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">for</span> i <span class=\"keyword\">in</span> s:</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> i==<span class=\"string\">&#x27;Z&#x27;</span>:</span><br><span class=\"line\">        f+=<span class=\"string\">&#x27;0&#x27;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">elif</span> i==<span class=\"string\">&#x27;N&#x27;</span>:</span><br><span class=\"line\">        f+=<span class=\"string\">&#x27;1&#x27;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">print(<span class=\"built_in\">len</span>(f))</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">print(<span class=\"built_in\">hex</span>(<span class=\"built_in\">int</span>(f,base=<span class=\"number\">2</span>)))</span><br><span class=\"line\">m=<span class=\"built_in\">int</span>(f,base=<span class=\"number\">2</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">print(m)</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n","text":"sherlock附件为一篇小说，首先采用搜索方法，直接搜索ｆｌａｇ，并没有什么发现，但是 [Figure] ","link":"","raw":null,"photos":[],"categories":[],"tags":[]},{"title":"","slug":"zhuanlunji","date":"2020-12-22T11:58:06.197Z","updated":"2020-12-27T12:39:23.156Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/zhuanlunji.json","excerpt":"","keywords":null,"cover":"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20201222184644544.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3dlaXhpbl80NjIyNzAxNg==,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70#pic_center","content":"<p><a href=\"https://adworld.xctf.org.cn/task/answer?type=crypto&number=5&grade=0&id=5113&page=1\">转轮机加密</a><br>首先查看附件信息，一种神奇的加密方式</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>1:  &lt; ZWAXJGDLUBVIQHKYPNTCRMOSFE &lt;<br>2:  &lt; KPBELNACZDTRXMJQOYHGVSFUWI &lt;<br>3:  &lt; BDMAIZVRNSJUWFHTEQGYXPLOCK &lt;<br>4:  &lt; RPLNDVHGFCUKTEBSXQYIZMJWAO &lt;<br>5:  &lt; IHFRLABEUOTSGJVDKCPMNZQWXY &lt;<br>6:  &lt; AMKGHIWPNYCJBFZDRUSLOQXVET &lt;<br>7:  &lt; GWTHSPYBXIZULVKMRAFDCEONJQ &lt;<br>8:  &lt; NOZUTWDCVRJLXKISEFAPMYGHBQ &lt;<br>9:  &lt; XPLTDSRFHENYVUBMCQWAOIKZGJ &lt;<br>10: &lt; UDNAJFBOWTGVRSCZQKELMXYIHP &lt;<br>11： &lt; MNBVCXZQWERTPOIUYALSKDJFHG &lt;<br>12： &lt; LVNCMXZPQOWEIURYTASBKJDFHG &lt;<br>13： &lt; JZQAWSXCDERFVBGTYHNUMKILOP &lt;<br>密钥为：2,3,7,5,13,12,9,1,8,10,4,11,6<br>密文为：NFQKSEVOQOFNP</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>题目中给出的是 提示转轮机 杰弗逊 经过查询可知杰弗逊转轮机加密方法，<br><a href=\"http://foreversong.cn/archives/138\">大佬给的解密原理</a></p>\n<p>利用原理写出python脚本。</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br><span class=\"line\">26</span><br><span class=\"line\">27</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">a=[ <span class=\"string\">&#x27;ZWAXJGDLUBVIQHKYPNTCRMOSFE&#x27;</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">&#x27;KPBELNACZDTRXMJQOYHGVSFUWI&#x27;</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">&#x27;BDMAIZVRNSJUWFHTEQGYXPLOCK&#x27;</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">&#x27;RPLNDVHGFCUKTEBSXQYIZMJWAO&#x27;</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">&#x27;IHFRLABEUOTSGJVDKCPMNZQWXY&#x27;</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">&#x27;AMKGHIWPNYCJBFZDRUSLOQXVET&#x27;</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">&#x27;GWTHSPYBXIZULVKMRAFDCEONJQ&#x27;</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">&#x27;NOZUTWDCVRJLXKISEFAPMYGHBQ&#x27;</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">&#x27;XPLTDSRFHENYVUBMCQWAOIKZGJ&#x27;</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">&#x27;UDNAJFBOWTGVRSCZQKELMXYIHP&#x27;</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">&#x27;MNBVCXZQWERTPOIUYALSKDJFHG&#x27;</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">&#x27;LVNCMXZPQOWEIURYTASBKJDFHG&#x27;</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">&#x27;JZQAWSXCDERFVBGTYHNUMKILOP&#x27;</span>]</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">key=[<span class=\"number\">2</span>,<span class=\"number\">3</span>,<span class=\"number\">7</span>,<span class=\"number\">5</span>,<span class=\"number\">13</span>,<span class=\"number\">12</span>,<span class=\"number\">9</span>,<span class=\"number\">1</span>,<span class=\"number\">8</span>,<span class=\"number\">10</span>,<span class=\"number\">4</span>,<span class=\"number\">11</span>,<span class=\"number\">6</span>]</span><br><span class=\"line\">table=[]</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">for</span> i <span class=\"keyword\">in</span> key:</span><br><span class=\"line\">    table.append(<span class=\"built_in\">list</span>(a[i-<span class=\"number\">1</span>]))</span><br><span class=\"line\">s=<span class=\"built_in\">list</span>(<span class=\"string\">&#x27;NFQKSEVOQOFNP&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">for</span> i <span class=\"keyword\">in</span> <span class=\"built_in\">range</span>(<span class=\"number\">0</span>,<span class=\"built_in\">len</span>(s)):</span><br><span class=\"line\">    index=table[i].index(s[i])</span><br><span class=\"line\">    temp=table[i][<span class=\"number\">0</span>:index]</span><br><span class=\"line\">    table[i][<span class=\"number\">0</span>:index]=[]</span><br><span class=\"line\">    table[i]+=temp</span><br><span class=\"line\">    print(table[i])</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">for</span> i <span class=\"keyword\">in</span> table:</span><br><span class=\"line\">    print(<span class=\"built_in\">chr</span>(<span class=\"built_in\">ord</span>(i[<span class=\"number\">17</span>])+<span class=\"number\">32</span>),end=<span class=\"string\">&#x27;&#x27;</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20201222184644544.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3dlaXhpbl80NjIyNzAxNg==,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70#pic_center\" alt=\"得到结果如图\"><br>有意义的明文为：fireinthehole<br>就是flag</p>\n","text":"转轮机加密<br>首先查看附件信息，一种神奇的加密方式1:  &lt; ZWAXJGDLUBVIQHKYPNTCRMOSFE &lt;<br>2:  &lt; KPBELNACZDTRXMJQOYHGVSFUWI &lt;<br>3:  &lt; BDMAIZVRNSJUWFHT","link":"","raw":null,"photos":[],"categories":[],"tags":[]},{"title":"","slug":"normalrsa","date":"2020-12-22T11:57:32.313Z","updated":"2020-12-22T11:57:50.165Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/normalrsa.json","excerpt":"","keywords":null,"cover":"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20201222185517887.png#pic_center","content":"<p><a href=\"https://adworld.xctf.org.cn/task/answer?type=crypto&number=5&grade=0&id=5115&page=1\">Normal RSA</a></p>\n<p>得到的附件为如图：<br><img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20201222185517887.png#pic_center\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\"><br>.pem为存放密钥的文件，.enc为加密文件<br>使用</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>openssl rsa -text -modulus -pubin -in pubkey.pem </p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/2020122219054912.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3dlaXhpbl80NjIyNzAxNg==,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70#pic_center\" alt=\"截图\"></p>\n<p> 得到n后使用<a href=\"http://www.factordb.com/\">factordb</a><br> 分解得到p和q.<br> 在进行正常的RSA操作。<br> 并利用crypto库中的构造输出密钥的方法，输出对应的privatekey.pem<br> 实现过程的脚本 如下：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">import</span> gmpy2</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">from</span> Crypto.PublicKey <span class=\"keyword\">import</span> RSA</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">p=gmpy2.mpz(<span class=\"number\">275127860351348928173285174381581152299</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\">q=gmpy2.mpz(<span class=\"number\">319576316814478949870590164193048041239</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">n=gmpy2.mpz(<span class=\"number\">87924348264132406875276140514499937145050893665602592992418171647042491658461</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\">e=<span class=\"number\">65537</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">fai=(p-<span class=\"number\">1</span>)*(q-<span class=\"number\">1</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">print(p*q)</span><br><span class=\"line\">d=gmpy2.invert(e,fai)</span><br><span class=\"line\">print(d)</span><br><span class=\"line\">p=<span class=\"number\">275127860351348928173285174381581152299</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">q=<span class=\"number\">319576316814478949870590164193048041239</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">fai=(p-<span class=\"number\">1</span>)*(q-<span class=\"number\">1</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\">n=<span class=\"number\">87924348264132406875276140514499937145050893665602592992418171647042491658461</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">d=<span class=\"number\">10866948760844599168252082612378495977388271279679231539839049698621994994673</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">privatekey=RSA.construct((n,e,d,p,q))</span><br><span class=\"line\">Key=privatekey.export_key()</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">with</span> <span class=\"built_in\">open</span>(<span class=\"string\">&#x27;prikey.pem&#x27;</span>,<span class=\"string\">&#x27;wb&#x27;</span>) <span class=\"keyword\">as</span> fp:</span><br><span class=\"line\">    fp.write(Key)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>得到解密密钥后，再一次使用openssl库，进行解密。<br>使用命令</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>openssl  reautl -decrypt -in flag.enc -inkey -private.key</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20201222192715102.png#pic_center\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\"></p>\n<p>得到明文flag.</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>使用RSATools可以更快解决，以后会继续研究RSATools的基本方法。</p>\n</blockquote>\n","text":"Normal RSA得到的附件为如图：<br> [Figure] 得到明文flag.使用RSATools可以更快解决，以后会继续研究RSATools的基本方法。","link":"","raw":null,"photos":[],"categories":[],"tags":[]},{"title":"","slug":"ecc","date":"2020-12-22T11:57:14.851Z","updated":"2020-12-22T11:57:19.106Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/ecc.json","excerpt":"","keywords":null,"cover":null,"content":"<p><a href=\"https://adworld.xctf.org.cn/task/answer?type=crypto&number=5&grade=0&id=5116&page=1\">ECC</a><br>第一次做椭圆曲线公钥加密方法，了解了一些ECC公钥加密的原理，</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>已知椭圆曲线加密Ep(a,b)参数为<br>p = 15424654874903<br>a = 16546484<br>b = 4548674875<br>G(6478678675,5636379357093)<br>私钥为<br>k = 546768<br>求公钥K(x,y)</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>根据博客学习了ECC公钥的加密原理<a href=\"https://www.cnblogs.com/Kalafinaian/p/7392505.html\">ECC</a></p>\n<p>根据题目与ECC的性质，可以构建脚本实现解密过程：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">Gx = <span class=\"number\">6478678675</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">Gy = <span class=\"number\">5636379357093</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">a = <span class=\"number\">16546484</span> </span><br><span class=\"line\">b = <span class=\"number\">4548674875</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">p = <span class=\"number\">15424654874903</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">k = <span class=\"number\">546768</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">x = Gx</span><br><span class=\"line\">y = Gy</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">for</span> i <span class=\"keyword\">in</span> <span class=\"built_in\">range</span>(k-<span class=\"number\">1</span>):</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> (x==Gx <span class=\"keyword\">and</span> y==Gy):</span><br><span class=\"line\">        inv = <span class=\"built_in\">pow</span>(<span class=\"number\">2</span>*Gy, p-<span class=\"number\">2</span>,p)</span><br><span class=\"line\">        temp = (<span class=\"number\">3</span>*Gx*Gx+a)*inv%p</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">else</span>:</span><br><span class=\"line\">        inv = <span class=\"built_in\">pow</span>((x-Gx), p-<span class=\"number\">2</span>,p)</span><br><span class=\"line\">        temp = (y-Gy)*inv%p</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">    xr = (temp*temp-Gx-x)%p</span><br><span class=\"line\">    yr = (temp*(x-xr)-y)%p</span><br><span class=\"line\"> <span class=\"comment\">#print(i,xr,yr)</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    x = xr</span><br><span class=\"line\">    y = yr</span><br><span class=\"line\">print(x+y)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n\n","text":"ECC<br>第一次做椭圆曲线公钥加密方法，了解了一些ECC公钥加密的原理，已知椭圆曲线加密Ep(a,b)参数为<br>p = 15424654874903<br>a = 16546484<br>b = 4548674875<br>G(6478678675,56363793570","link":"","raw":null,"photos":[],"categories":[],"tags":[]},{"title":"","slug":"xctf2","date":"2020-12-15T08:30:54.958Z","updated":"2020-12-15T08:52:56.794Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/xctf2.json","excerpt":"","keywords":null,"cover":null,"content":"<hr>\n<h2 id=\"XCTF-幂数加密\"><a href=\"#XCTF-幂数加密\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"XCTF-幂数加密\"></a>XCTF-幂数加密</h2><p><a href=\"https://adworld.xctf.org.cn/task/answer?type=crypto&number=5&grade=0&id=5120&page=1\">XCTF-原题目链接-幂数加密</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"思路\"><a href=\"#思路\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"思路\"></a>思路</h2><p>下载附件得到一串数字<br>8842101220480224404014224202480122<br>没有头绪，于是采用”题目攻击“<br>搜索幂数加密得到二进制加密方法，得到</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>二进制幂数加密法就是应用这个原理，由于英文字母只有26个字母，由公式可知，只要2的0、1、2、3、4、5次幂就可以表示31个单元。通过用二进制幂数表示字母序号数来加密。例如<br>明文： d o n o t p u l l a l l y o u r e g g s i n o n e b a s k e t<br>字母序号：4 15 14 15 20 16 21 12 12 1 12 12 25 15 21 18 5 7 7 19 9 14 15 14 5 2 1 19 11 5 20<br>由于4=2^2 所以D加密过之后是2；15=2^0+2^1+2^2+2^3所以O加密后是0123。同理得到上述明文的加密后的密文<br>密文：2 0123/123 0123 24/4 024 23 23/0 23 23/034 0123 024 14/02 012 012 014/03 123 /0123 123 02/1 0 014 013 02 24<br>其中空格表示字母的间隔，/表示单词的间隔。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>并没有什么用。于是放弃了，看了题解。</p>\n<p>根据题解得到题目有提到一共八个字母，那么原数字可以看成8段，恰好7个0，那么一段一个数字，每个数字个位数字之和都小于26（有点幂数加密的味道），可以看成是偏移量，就可以得到明文。</p>\n<p>脚本如下</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">ans=[<span class=\"number\">88421</span>,<span class=\"number\">122</span>,<span class=\"number\">48</span>,<span class=\"number\">2244</span>,<span class=\"number\">4</span>,<span class=\"number\">142242</span>,<span class=\"number\">248</span>,<span class=\"number\">122</span>]</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">for</span> i <span class=\"keyword\">in</span> ans:</span><br><span class=\"line\">    temp=<span class=\"number\">0</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">while</span> i:</span><br><span class=\"line\">        temp+=i%<span class=\"number\">10</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        i//=<span class=\"number\">10</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    temp=<span class=\"built_in\">ord</span>(<span class=\"string\">&#x27;A&#x27;</span>)+temp-<span class=\"number\">1</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    print(<span class=\"built_in\">chr</span>(temp),end=<span class=\"string\">&#x27;&#x27;</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n","text":"XCTF-幂数加密XCTF-原题目链接-幂数加密思路下载附件得到一串数字<br>8842101220480224404014224202480122<br>没有头绪，于是采用”题目攻击“<br>搜索幂数加密得到二进制加密方法，得到二进制幂数加密法就是应用这个原理，由于英文字母只有","link":"","raw":null,"photos":[],"categories":[],"tags":[]},{"title":"","slug":"easychallenge","date":"2020-12-15T08:29:54.453Z","updated":"2020-12-15T08:53:00.740Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/easychallenge.json","excerpt":"","keywords":null,"cover":null,"content":"<hr>\n<h2 id=\"easychallenge\"><a href=\"#easychallenge\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"easychallenge\"></a>easychallenge</h2><p><a href=\"https://adworld.xctf.org.cn/task/answer?type=crypto&number=5&grade=0&id=5119&page=1\">XCTF-easychallenge</a></p>\n<p>下载附件得到是一个pyc文件，对pyc代码反编译，可以得到其python代码</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br><span class=\"line\">26</span><br><span class=\"line\">27</span><br><span class=\"line\">28</span><br><span class=\"line\">29</span><br><span class=\"line\">30</span><br><span class=\"line\">31</span><br><span class=\"line\">32</span><br><span class=\"line\">33</span><br><span class=\"line\">34</span><br><span class=\"line\">35</span><br><span class=\"line\">36</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># !/usr/bin/env python</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># visit http://tool.lu/pyc/ for more information</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">import</span> base64</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">def</span> <span class=\"title\">encode1</span>(<span class=\"params\">ans</span>):</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    s = <span class=\"string\">&#x27;&#x27;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">for</span> i <span class=\"keyword\">in</span> ans:</span><br><span class=\"line\">        x = <span class=\"built_in\">ord</span>(i) ^ <span class=\"number\">36</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        x = x + <span class=\"number\">25</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        s += <span class=\"built_in\">chr</span>(x)</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> s</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">def</span> <span class=\"title\">encode2</span>(<span class=\"params\">ans</span>):</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    s = <span class=\"string\">&#x27;&#x27;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">for</span> i <span class=\"keyword\">in</span> ans:</span><br><span class=\"line\">        x = <span class=\"built_in\">ord</span>(i) + <span class=\"number\">36</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        x = x ^ <span class=\"number\">36</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        s += <span class=\"built_in\">chr</span>(x)</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> s</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">def</span> <span class=\"title\">encode3</span>(<span class=\"params\">ans</span>):</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> base64.b32encode(ans)</span><br><span class=\"line\">flag = <span class=\"string\">&#x27; &#x27;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">print(<span class=\"string\">&#x27;Please Input your flag:&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\">flag = <span class=\"built_in\">input</span>()</span><br><span class=\"line\">final = <span class=\"string\">&#x27;UC7KOWVXWVNKNIC2XCXKHKK2W5NLBKNOUOSK3LNNVWW3E===&#x27;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">if</span> encode3(encode2(encode1(flag))) == final:</span><br><span class=\"line\">    print(<span class=\"string\">&#x27;correct&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">else</span>:</span><br><span class=\"line\">    print(<span class=\"string\">&#x27;wrong&#x27;</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>对于python源码，我们发现其使用了base32编码，然后又进行了异或的编码操作，首先对于逆向final，就可以得到答案。在求解过程，base32的解码方式，出现了很多问题，一直显示无法解码，通过wp活动base32的编码要求，就能得到答案。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/questions/19699367/for-line-in-results-in-unicodedecodeerror-utf-8-codec-cant-decode-byte\">base32无法编码的解决方法</a></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">import</span> base64</span><br><span class=\"line\">final = <span class=\"string\">&#x27;UC7KOWVXWVNKNIC2XCXKHKK2W5NLBKNOUOSK3LNNVWW3E===&#x27;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">st=base64.b32decode(final).decode(<span class=\"string\">&#x27;ISO-8859-1&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\">s=<span class=\"string\">&#x27;&#x27;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">for</span> i <span class=\"keyword\">in</span> st:</span><br><span class=\"line\">    temp=<span class=\"built_in\">ord</span>(i)</span><br><span class=\"line\">    temp=temp^<span class=\"number\">36</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    temp-=<span class=\"number\">36</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    temp-=<span class=\"number\">25</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    temp=temp^<span class=\"number\">36</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    s+=<span class=\"built_in\">chr</span>(temp)</span><br><span class=\"line\">print(s)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n","text":"easychallengeXCTF-easychallenge下载附件得到是一个pyc文件，对pyc代码反编译，可以得到其python代码1<br>2<br>3<br>4<br>5<br>6<br>7<br>8<br>9<br>10<br>11<br>12<br>13<br>14","link":"","raw":null,"photos":[],"categories":[],"tags":[]},{"title":"","slug":"xctf1","date":"2020-12-15T08:14:57.952Z","updated":"2020-12-15T08:52:58.806Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/xctf1.json","excerpt":"","keywords":null,"cover":"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20201213201117133.png","content":"<hr>\n<h2 id=\"XCTF混合编码\"><a href=\"#XCTF混合编码\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"XCTF混合编码\"></a>XCTF混合编码</h2><p><a href=\"https://adworld.xctf.org.cn/task/answer?type=crypto&number=5&grade=0&id=5118&page=1\">XCTF混合编码</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"过程\"><a href=\"#过程\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"过程\"></a>过程</h2><p>下载附件后得到一段很长的字符串</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p></p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>发现最后为==，说明很有可能采用了base64编码，于是使用python进行base64解码，得到新的字符串</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20201213201117133.png\" alt=\"解码结果\"><br>查询这种编码方式得到为Webdings<br>对照表<br><a href=\"https://blog.csdn.net/weixin_33989780/article/details/85868511?utm_medium=distribute.pc_relevant.none-task-blog-BlogCommendFromMachineLearnPai2-4.control&amp;depth_1-utm_source=distribute.pc_relevant.none-task-blog-BlogCommendFromMachineLearnPai2-4.control\">https://blog.csdn.net/weixin_33989780/article/details/85868511?utm_medium=distribute.pc_relevant.none-task-blog-BlogCommendFromMachineLearnPai2-4.control&amp;depth_1-utm_source=distribute.pc_relevant.none-task-blog-BlogCommendFromMachineLearnPai2-4.control</a></p>\n<p>使用python将将这种编码方式转化为对应字母，发现仍然是乱码</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>LzExOS8xMDEvMTA4Lzk5LzExMS8xMDkvMTAxLzExNi8xMTEvOTcvMTE2LzExNi85Ny85OS8xMDcvOTcvMTEwLzEwMC8xMDAvMTAxLzEwMi8xMDEvMTEwLzk5LzEwMS8xMTkvMTExLzExNC8xMDgvMTAw</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>发现不符合MD5加密规则，首先尝试base64，发现可以得到有意义的字符串，得到答案。</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">import</span> base64</span><br><span class=\"line\">s=<span class=\"string\">r&#x27;&#x27;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">st=base64.b64decode(s).decode(<span class=\"string\">&quot;utf-8&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\">l=<span class=\"built_in\">list</span>(st.split(<span class=\"string\">&#x27;;&#x27;</span>))</span><br><span class=\"line\">l.pop(<span class=\"built_in\">len</span>(l)-<span class=\"number\">1</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\">ans=[]</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">for</span> i <span class=\"keyword\">in</span> l:</span><br><span class=\"line\">    ans.append(<span class=\"built_in\">chr</span>(<span class=\"built_in\">int</span>(i[<span class=\"number\">2</span>:])))</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">print(l)</span><br><span class=\"line\">t=<span class=\"string\">&#x27;&#x27;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">for</span> i <span class=\"keyword\">in</span> ans:</span><br><span class=\"line\">   t+=i</span><br><span class=\"line\">print(t)</span><br><span class=\"line\">st=base64.b64decode(t).decode(<span class=\"string\">&quot;utf-8&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\">t=<span class=\"built_in\">list</span>(st.split(<span class=\"string\">r&#x27;/&#x27;</span>))</span><br><span class=\"line\">t.pop(<span class=\"number\">0</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">for</span> i <span class=\"keyword\">in</span> t:</span><br><span class=\"line\">    print(<span class=\"built_in\">chr</span>(<span class=\"built_in\">int</span>(i)),end=<span class=\"string\">&#x27;&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n","text":"XCTF混合编码XCTF混合编码过程下载附件后得到一段很长的字符串JiM3NjsmIzEyMjsmIzY5OyYjMTIwOyYjNzk7JiM4MzsmIzU2OyYjMTIwOyYjNzc7JiM2ODsmIzY5OyYjMTE4OyYjNzc7JiM4NDsmIzY1OyY","link":"","raw":null,"photos":[],"categories":[],"tags":[]},{"title":"Hello World","slug":"hello-world","date":"2020-12-10T07:50:23.196Z","updated":"2020-12-10T08:04:28.221Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/hello-world.json","excerpt":"","keywords":null,"cover":null,"content":"<p>Welcome to <a href=\"https://hexo.io/\">Hexo</a>! This is your very first post. Check <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/\">documentation</a> for more info. If you get any problems when using Hexo, you can find the answer in <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/troubleshooting.html\">troubleshooting</a> or you can ask me on <a href=\"https://github.com/hexojs/hexo/issues\">GitHub</a>.</p>\n<h2 id=\"摸鱼大法好\"><a href=\"#摸鱼大法好\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"摸鱼大法好\"></a>摸鱼大法好</h2><h2 id=\"Quick-Start\"><a href=\"#Quick-Start\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Quick Start\"></a>Quick Start</h2><h3 id=\"Create-a-new-post\"><a href=\"#Create-a-new-post\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Create a new post\"></a>Create a new post</h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ hexo new <span class=\"string\">&quot;My New Post&quot;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>More info: <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/writing.html\">Writing</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"Run-server\"><a href=\"#Run-server\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Run server\"></a>Run server</h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ hexo server</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>More info: <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/server.html\">Server</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"Generate-static-files\"><a href=\"#Generate-static-files\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Generate static files\"></a>Generate static files</h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ hexo generate</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>More info: <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/generating.html\">Generating</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"Deploy-to-remote-sites\"><a href=\"#Deploy-to-remote-sites\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Deploy to remote sites\"></a>Deploy to remote sites</h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ hexo deploy</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>More info: <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/one-command-deployment.html\">Deployment</a></p>\n","text":"Welcome to Hexo! This is your very first post. Check documentation for more info. If you get any problems when using Hexo, you can find the ","link":"","raw":null,"photos":[],"categories":[],"tags":[]}]}